OL,3,CPressure on Starmer ramps up as
OL,4,CBurnham one step closer to challenge
OL,6,FThe prospect of a leadership challenge
OL,7,Fto Sir Keir Starmer is looming closer
OL,8,Fafter Andy Burnham was cleared to run
OL,9,Ffor selection in the Makerfield by-
OL,10,Felection.
OL,12,FThe Greater Manchester mayor is
OL,13,Fseeking to replace Josh Simons, who is
OL,14,Fstanding down as an MP to make way for
OL,15,FMr Burnham to return to Parliament.
OL,17,FLabour's ruling body, the National
OL,18,FExecutive Committee (NEC), has granted
OL,19,FMr Burnham permission to stand in the
OL,20,Fselection process.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
