OL,3,CPressure on Starmer ramps up as
OL,4,CBurnham one step closer to challenge
OL,6,FApplications close on Monday and the
OL,7,FNEC will endorse a candidate on
OL,8,FThursday. June 18 is thought to be the
OL,9,Fearliest date a by-election could take
OL,10,Fplace.
OL,12,FIf he is successfully elected, Mr
OL,13,FBurnham is widely expected to
OL,14,Fchallenge Sir Keir for the party
OL,15,Fleadership.
OL,17,FWhile Makerfield is typically a safe
OL,18,Fseat for Labour, the party expects a
OL,19,Fstiff challenge from Reform UK this
OL,20,Ftime around.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
