OL,3,CPressure on Starmer ramps up as
OL,4,CBurnham one step closer to challenge
OL,6,FMr Simons secured a majority of just
OL,7,F5,399 over Nigel Farage's party at the
OL,8,F2024 general election.
OL,10,FSince then, Labour's polling collapse
OL,11,Fand Reform's surge have seen their
OL,12,Fpositions reverse.
OL,14,FThis month's local elections saw
OL,15,FReform win every council ward in the
OL,16,FMakerfield constituency, securing
OL,17,Faround half the vote, while Labour won
OL,18,Fonly a little more than a quarter.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
