OL,3,CPressure on Starmer ramps up as
OL,4,CBurnham one step closer to challenge
OL,6,FCandidate selection processes are
OL,7,Falready under way for Reform UK and
OL,8,Fthe Greens.
OL,10,FOn Saturday, Wes Streeting ` who quit
OL,11,Fas health secretary this week but
OL,12,Fstopped short of triggering a
OL,13,Fleadership contest ` is set to make
OL,14,Fhis first public appearance since he
OL,15,Fresigned when he speaks at a
OL,16,Fconference.
OL,18,FMr Streeting is among those who have
OL,19,Fbacked Mr Burnham's bid to fight the
OL,20,Fimpending by-election, saying Labour
OL,21,Fneeds "our best players on the pitch".
OL,26,@}D@GOU}D@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
