OL,3,CPressure on Starmer ramps up as
OL,4,CBurnham one step closer to challenge
OL,6,FAllies of the Ilford North MP have
OL,7,Fsaid he would be a candidate in any
OL,8,Fforthcoming leadership battle.
OL,10,FThey added Mr Streeting had made clear
OL,11,Fin his resignation letter that he
OL,12,Fwanted a contest to feature "the
OL,13,Fbroadest set of candidates possible".
OL,15,FIf he did not step down, Sir Keir
OL,16,Fwould automatically be on the ballot
OL,17,Fpaper in any Labour leadership race,
OL,18,Fand Downing Street has continued to
OL,19,Finsist that he would fight any effort
OL,20,Fto oust him.
OL,26,@tD@]OUuD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
