OL,3,CPressure on Starmer ramps up as
OL,4,CBurnham one step closer to challenge
OL,6,FThe Government's defence investment
OL,7,Fplan has been long delayed and Defence
OL,8,FSecretary John Healey has been pushing
OL,9,Fprivately for a substantial uplift for
OL,10,Fsome time, which he sees as essential
OL,11,Fto meet the rising threats facing the
OL,12,FUK, it is understood.
OL,14,FA Government spokesperson said: "The
OL,15,Fdefence investment plan will deliver
OL,16,Fthe best kit and technology into the
OL,17,Fhands of our frontline forces at
OL,18,Fspeed, while investing in and growing
OL,19,Fthe UK economy.
OL,26,@vD@aOU
